One Clean Description

The strategy trains an LSTM model on lagged quarterly changes in firm fundamentals to identify stocks likely to experience price adjustments following new information. We trade these signals by purchasing near-ATM options and dynamically delta hedging with the underlying equity, allowing the portfolio to profit primarily from convex price movements and realized volatility rather than directional market exposure.

